<refsect1 id='examples'><title>EXAMPLES</title>

<para>
  Create a cpt-file topobath.cpt from topo.cpt and bath.cpt
</para>

<programlisting>
  cptcat -v -o topobath.cpt topo.cpt bath.cpt
</programlisting>

